18
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:38,130
Siapa yang begitu lancang?

19
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:39,759
Berani mengacau tokoku.

20
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,120
Kakak.

21
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:43,719
Kakakmu?

22
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:45,719
Kak.

23
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:48,120
Kenapa kakakmu terlihat aneh?

24
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,120
Apa dia minum arak?

25
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,280
Ka… Kakakku tak pernah minum arak.

26
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:03,639
Tampang kakakmu
terlihat sangat aneh.

27
00:03:04,639 --> 00:03:07,439
Dari mana kau dapatkan bahan
untuk pedang berhargamu ini?

28
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:11,280
-Kak!
-Hati-hati!

29
00:03:12,439 --> 00:03:12,960
Kakek.

30
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:13,919
Kakek.

31
00:03:14,439 --> 00:03:15,639
Kakek, kau tak apa, 'kan?

32
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:19,280
Yin Xiao!

33
00:03:19,599 --> 00:03:20,280
Apa kau gila?

34
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,800
Kau mana boleh begitu
pada orang tua!

35
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:23,180
Jika kau emosi, lampiaskan padaku…

36
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:25,599
Aku…

37
00:03:26,159 --> 00:03:26,520
Aku…

38
00:03:27,439 --> 00:03:27,800
Aku…

39
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,250
Aku sangat kecewa padamu.

40
00:03:30,420 --> 00:03:30,970
Apa kau tahu?

41
00:03:32,599 --> 00:03:33,599
Kau tak kuat minum arak.

42
00:03:33,599 --> 00:03:35,230
Kelak, jangan minum arak
diam-diam lagi.

43
00:03:35,319 --> 00:03:37,130
Tak… Tak pantas
minum terlalu banyak.

44
00:03:38,439 --> 00:03:39,380
Huotu Xin, kau tak apa, 'kan?

45
00:03:48,319 --> 00:03:49,010
Tak apa, 'kan?

46
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,730
-Ayo pergi!
-Jalan!

47
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:06,530
Jalan!

48
00:04:19,639 --> 00:04:20,020
Kak.

49
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,930
Kakakku sebenarnya kenapa?

50
00:04:28,399 --> 00:04:29,820
Dia pasti terkena obat halusinasi!

51
00:04:30,079 --> 00:04:31,700
Obat halusinasi? Apa bisa diobati?

52
00:04:32,319 --> 00:04:33,020
Bisa.

53
00:04:33,279 --> 00:04:34,610
Obat penawarku ada di atas.

54
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:35,530
Di atas?

55
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,220
Di atas?

56
00:04:50,060 --> 00:04:51,780
Payungku ini takutnya
tak akan kuat lagi.

57
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:53,800
Jadi, kita harus
bagaimana sekarang?

58
00:04:54,839 --> 00:04:55,530
Pakai gelang.

59
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:58,100
Cepat pakai! Kalian berdua!

60
00:04:59,759 --> 00:05:00,260
Lalu?

61
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,340
Benturkan!

62
00:05:01,770 --> 00:05:02,240
Benturkan.

63
00:05:10,199 --> 00:05:11,100
Jangan lukai Kakakku.

64
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:34,240
Bagaimana cara pakainya?

65
00:05:34,439 --> 00:05:35,530
Pakai air!

66
00:05:35,839 --> 00:05:37,480
Air? Ba… Bagaimana cara pakainya?

67
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:38,340
Air? Bagaimana…

68
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:15,260
Kak?

69
00:06:17,279 --> 00:06:17,700
Yin…

70
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:20,170
Yin… Yin Zhuang.

71
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:26,050
Kak.

72
00:06:29,079 --> 00:06:30,260
Mahakaryaku.

73
00:06:31,879 --> 00:06:33,900
Sungguh tak ternilai harganya!

74
00:06:35,319 --> 00:06:35,730
Aku…

75
00:06:41,519 --> 00:06:42,850
Lapor, Raja, Perdana Menteri Fei.

76
00:06:43,399 --> 00:06:44,780
Pasukan Zhu Xi sudah masuk Zhaodu.

77
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,220
Zhu Xi hanya membawa
seratusan orang.

78
00:06:54,140 --> 00:06:56,450
Namun, kita harus kerahkan
seluruh pasukan kota berjaga.

79
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:00,410
Bukankah ini terlalu berlebihan?

80
00:07:01,439 --> 00:07:04,830
"Singa mengincar kelinci"
juga mengerahkan seluruh tenaga.

81
00:07:05,199 --> 00:07:06,580
Kali ini, Zhu Xi datang begitu cepat.

82
00:07:08,020 --> 00:07:09,180
Takutnya sudah lama bersiap.

83
00:07:12,020 --> 00:07:13,080
Hadapi musuh yang datang.

84
00:07:13,839 --> 00:07:15,220
Kau sudah lama merencanakannya,…

85
00:07:16,220 --> 00:07:17,260
…maka laksanakanlah.

86
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:20,480
Akan kujaga Kota Kekaisaran
dengan baik.

87
00:07:20,650 --> 00:07:22,080
Sudah begitu lama kurencanakan.

88
00:07:23,639 --> 00:07:24,340
Akhirnya,…

89
00:07:25,879 --> 00:07:27,100
…mereka semua datang.

90
00:07:28,079 --> 00:07:28,610
Yuan Yi!

91
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,360
Sebaiknya aku keluar dulu.

92
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:35,730
Tak apa.

93
00:07:36,460 --> 00:07:37,440
Ada apa kau mencariku?

94
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,780
Kudengar Zhu Xi sudah tiba.

95
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:42,020
Orang yang ingin membunuhmu
telah muncul.

96
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:43,930
Apa kau tak takut?

97
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,290
Aku tak takut.

98
00:07:48,439 --> 00:07:50,850
Aku ingin lihat, bagaimana
tampang dia sebenarnya.

99
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,460
Sakit.

100
00:07:55,639 --> 00:07:56,660
Sakit. Sakit!

101
00:07:58,800 --> 00:07:59,780
Kenapa bisa begini?

102
00:08:01,639 --> 00:08:02,410
Aku juga tak tahu.

103
00:08:04,839 --> 00:08:05,530
Bagaimana jika…

104
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:08,970
…kita coba lagi?

105
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,490
Sakit.

106
00:08:25,319 --> 00:08:26,410
Bagaimana ini?

107
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:27,930
Ini adalah mas kawinku.

108
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:29,200
Bagaimana jika…

109
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:32,130
…kita istirahat dulu sebentar?

110
00:08:32,879 --> 00:08:33,770
Minum obat ini.

111
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:36,970
Bisa mengobati halusinasi
yang kau alami.

112
00:08:44,399 --> 00:08:45,100
Sudah membaik?

113
00:08:46,159 --> 00:08:47,010
Sungguh maaf.

114
00:08:47,519 --> 00:08:49,820
Demi menolong Yin Zhuang,
aku hampir melukai Tuan.

115
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:51,540
Bahkan aku merusak tokomu.

116
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:52,940
Tak masalah.

117
00:08:53,639 --> 00:08:55,280
Sekalian mencoba
sepasang gelang itu.

118
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:01,460
Kota Pingting ini sangat kacau.

119
00:09:01,799 --> 00:09:04,130
Apa Tuan Muda
menyinggung seseorang?

120
00:09:05,039 --> 00:09:05,770
Aku juga tak tahu.

121
00:09:07,290 --> 00:09:09,480
Terima kasih sudah buatkan
senjata untuk Yin Zhuang.

122
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:10,180
Jangan.

123
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:13,010
Malah aku yang harus
berterima kasih padamu.

124
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:15,650
Aku melihat adikmu
membawa dua potong…

125
00:09:16,159 --> 00:09:17,879
…batu kristal yang begitu berharga.

126
00:09:17,879 --> 00:09:19,970
Aku takut dirusak oleh
para pengrajin biasa.

127
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:23,100
Karena itu, tanganku
jadi terasa 'gatal'.

128
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:25,650
Bagaimana?

129
00:09:25,799 --> 00:09:26,610
Sepasang gelang itu…

130
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:28,420
…lumayan, 'kan?

131
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:31,420
Keahlian Tuan memang hebat.

132
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:36,650
Pembuat Senjata seperti Tuan
hanya sedikit di seluruh Suchuan.

133
00:09:38,679 --> 00:09:42,060
Namun, Tuan, kenapa bisa
tinggal di tempat ini?

134
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,940
Panjang bila kuceritakan.

135
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:58,650
Sungguh sangat menyakitkan.

136
00:09:59,679 --> 00:10:01,180
Kenapa bisa begini?

137
00:10:07,279 --> 00:10:08,180
Kau juga jangan cemas.

138
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,300
Pasti bisa dilepas.

139
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,060
Apa mungkin ini takdir?

140
00:10:22,679 --> 00:10:25,130
Pasti memang takdir.

141
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:29,300
Tuhan…

142
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,850
…juga tak mau kau menikahi
Weisheng Yan.

143
00:10:36,020 --> 00:10:36,950
Kakakmu sudah datang.

144
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:38,620
Waktunya kita pergi.

145
00:10:39,399 --> 00:10:40,650
Kak, kau tak apa, 'kan?

146
00:10:42,399 --> 00:10:44,340
Namun, gelangku…

147
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:48,990
Biarkan saja dia pakai dulu.

148
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:50,180
Apa?

149
00:10:50,759 --> 00:10:51,700
Setelah tiba di Zhaodu,…

150
00:10:51,700 --> 00:10:53,710
…kita masih bisa ambil dengan
memotong tangannya.

151
00:10:55,639 --> 00:10:56,420
Jangan khawatir.

152
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,340
Putrimu bisa mengobatimu.

153
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:06,460
Tadi kau bilang…

154
00:11:07,679 --> 00:11:09,060
…kau ingin membawaku ke Zhaodu?

155
00:11:09,799 --> 00:11:12,650
Kudengar Zhu Xi sudah berangkat
ke Zhaodu kemarin.

156
00:11:13,279 --> 00:11:16,820
Sejak Raja masa kini naik takhta,
Zhu Xi tak pernah muncul di Zhaodu.

157
00:11:17,799 --> 00:11:19,820
Kali ini dia pasti pergi
karena Linglong.

158
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:24,580
Tak hanya Zhu Xi, sepertinya
Weisheng Yan juga terlibat.

159
00:11:25,759 --> 00:11:28,650
Maksudmu Weisheng Yan
dan Zhu Xi juga bekerja sama?

160
00:11:29,919 --> 00:11:32,300
Weisheng Yan tak sesederhana itu.

161
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:35,620
Semua hal yang sebelumnya
kita alami di Pingting,…

162
00:11:35,790 --> 00:11:37,180
…sepertinya berkaitan dengannya.

163
00:11:38,799 --> 00:11:39,370
Bahkan…

164
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,340
…pernikahan kalian juga.

165
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:47,060
Kini, setelah menarik diri, aku baru
bisa lihat semuanya dengan jelas.

166
00:11:51,039 --> 00:11:51,580
Yin Xiao.

167
00:11:52,799 --> 00:11:56,420
Kau bilang, Zhu Xi sudah
mengejar sampai ke Zhaodu?

168
00:11:56,879 --> 00:11:59,700
Jika putrimu sungguh Dewi Ratu,…

169
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:03,580
…maka di Suchuan, tak ada lagi
tempat yang aman bagi putrimu.

170
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:07,130
Apa kau punya kabar terbaru
tentang Linglong?

171
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:10,250
Zhaodu akan segera
mengadakan Upacara Bisheng.

172
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:11,940
Upacara Bisheng?

173
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:13,850
Apa itu Upacara Bisheng?

174
00:12:14,180 --> 00:12:16,060
Upacara pemberian gelar Dewi
untuk Linglong.

175
00:12:16,279 --> 00:12:19,250
Jika dia berhasil, dia akan jadi
Dewi Ratu yang sesungguhnya.

176
00:12:19,799 --> 00:12:20,730
Jika gagal,…

177
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:24,610
…dia… Dia akan dihukum mati
dengan dianggap…

178
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:26,180
…sebagai siluman atau penipu.

179
00:12:31,639 --> 00:12:35,100
Bunuh Dewi Ratu di altar suci.

180
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:39,060
Dibandingkan dengan hal ini,
tak ada lagi hal lain…

181
00:12:41,399 --> 00:12:44,940
…yang lebih mengejutkan.

182
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:48,700
Zhu Xi ingin membunuh Linglong
saat Upacara Bisheng.

183
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:50,940
Kenapa?

184
00:12:52,420 --> 00:12:53,799
Demi hal mengejutkan atau takhta.

185
00:12:53,799 --> 00:12:55,600
Aku tak tahu. Pokoknya ini
adalah rencananya.

186
00:12:55,700 --> 00:12:57,830
Selama ratusan tahun ini,
Klan Yuan tak tergantikan…

187
00:12:58,519 --> 00:13:00,610
…hanya karena dia adalah
raja pilihan dewa.

188
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:05,420
Jika Zhu Xi bisa membunuh Dewi,
maka fondasi Klan Yuan akan goyah.

189
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:06,980
Dengan begini,…

190
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:10,170
…Klan Yuan bukan lagi
klan yang tak tergantikan.

191
00:13:10,640 --> 00:13:12,380
Ingin membunuh Dewi
saat Upacara Bisheng?

192
00:13:13,039 --> 00:13:14,350
Namun, tempat itu adalah Zhaodu.

193
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:17,540
Apalagi, jika Linglong
sungguh Dewi Ratu,…

194
00:13:18,519 --> 00:13:19,770
…Zhu Xi juga tak bisa melawannya.

195
00:13:20,120 --> 00:13:22,460
Dewi Ratu atau monster,
mereka yang anggap dia begitu.

196
00:13:25,759 --> 00:13:27,180
Aku bawa kalian menemui seseorang.

197
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:27,940
Siapa?

198
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:32,970
Yin Zhuang.

199
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:37,180
Kita batalkan pernikahanmu.

200
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:43,820
Soal putri Pak Tua Jia adalah
monster dari wabah 17 tahun lalu…

201
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:46,420
…sudah kukatakan pada bocah itu
sesuai yang kau mau.

202
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:48,420
Maaf, Kakek.

203
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:50,540
Aku membuatmu cemas lagi.

204
00:13:53,279 --> 00:13:54,220
Katakan pada Kakek.

205
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:56,370
Apa kau menyukainya?

206
00:13:57,919 --> 00:13:58,610
Kakek.

207
00:13:59,159 --> 00:14:00,250
Asal bicara apa?

208
00:14:02,399 --> 00:14:03,340
Selama bertahun-tahun,…

209
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:06,420
…entah berapa banyak pria
yang kau usir dari rumah ini.

210
00:14:06,690 --> 00:14:08,300
Pada awalnya,
aku masih menghitungnya.

211
00:14:08,759 --> 00:14:10,550
Akhirnya, aku sampai
tak mampu ingat lagi.

212
00:14:10,799 --> 00:14:14,940
Namun, sepertinya hanya dia saja
yang dekat dengan keluarga kita, 'kan?

213
00:14:16,159 --> 00:14:17,100
Mana ada.

214
00:14:20,480 --> 00:14:20,940
Gadis.

215
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:25,250
Aku tak tahu untuk apa
kau memancingnya.

216
00:14:25,759 --> 00:14:28,820
Namun, itu pasti hal
yang berbahaya, 'kan?

217
00:14:33,480 --> 00:14:34,890
Kau harus menjaganya dengan ketat.

218
00:14:35,020 --> 00:14:35,880
Jangan sampai nanti…

219
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:37,850
Nanti menyesal.

220
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:39,250
Kakek.

221
00:14:40,279 --> 00:14:41,850
Lihatlah, asal bicara terus.

222
00:14:49,879 --> 00:14:51,820
Raja dan Dewi Ratu tiba!

223
00:15:17,799 --> 00:15:19,770
Hormat, Raja.

224
00:15:20,600 --> 00:15:21,490
Semuanya, berdirilah.

225
00:15:22,519 --> 00:15:24,100
Terima kasih, Raja.

226
00:15:30,279 --> 00:15:33,100
Beberapa hari ini, bagaimana
hasil belajar kalian di Tianqi?

227
00:15:34,120 --> 00:15:34,820
Menjawab Raja.

228
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:38,010
Murid Perguruan Tianqi ajari kami
tentang keajaiban dari Dewi Ratu…

229
00:15:38,399 --> 00:15:39,890
…dan meneliti koleksi dinasti lalu.

230
00:15:40,450 --> 00:15:41,680
Mendapat banyak pengetahuan.

231
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:42,490
Bagus.

232
00:15:43,160 --> 00:15:44,540
Saat Bangsawan Pingjiang datang,…

233
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:47,570
…kalian boleh berbagi pengalaman
kalian beberapa hari ini dengannya,…

234
00:15:47,690 --> 00:15:49,650
…agar dia tak melewatkannya
karena telat datang.

235
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:52,250
Lapor!

236
00:15:55,639 --> 00:15:57,310
